{"TopicId":169414,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"[1.3.1] Octogon R.E.D - Rapid Explosive Desintegrator","CreatedByName":"EricPoehlsen","CreatedById":182872,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-09T22:59:46Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EricPoehlsen","CreatedById":182872,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-09T22:59:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Octogon R.E.D. - Rapid Explosive Desintegrator is a part that let\u0027s you abort your mission in style, by running a self destruct sequence. This is of course to protect the ground personnel and infrastructure from falling debris after a failed launch.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt adds a single part into the game, which resides within the \u003Cem\u003ECommand \u0026amp; Control\u003C/em\u003E tab.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd this part to a vessel that you might want to destroy on mission abort. More information on how to use it correctly can be found in the README.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can find the current state of the mod on\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/EricPoehlsen/Octogon_RapidExplosiveDesintegration\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGithub\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense (Short version):\u003Cbr\u003E\nCode: \u0027free\u0027 - CC-0 / MIT / WTFPL (use whichever suits your needs)\u003Cbr\u003E\nGraphic and text assets \u0026amp; game data (\u003Cem\u003EGameData/Octogon\u003C/em\u003E: CC-BY-NC-ND 3.0\u003Cbr\u003E\n(check LICENSE.md for details)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI started dabbling with creating a first mod and this is the result.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022red.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022578\u0022 src=\u0022https://eric-poehlsen.de/images/red.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis part destroys the vessel when aborting the mission so that ground personnel and infrastructure is not damaged by the failing rocket.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-01-10T15:21:38Z\u0022 title=\u002201/10/2018 03:21  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 10, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by EricPoehlsen\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ELicense information updated (just free licenses now)\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-09T23:07:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi, \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182872-ericpoehlsen/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022182872\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/182872-ericpoehlsen/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@EricPoehlsen\u003C/a\u003E! I don\u0027t think we\u0027ve met yet! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EOne thing important to remember is that the forum requires a license included with all mods, and also mentioned in the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E, too. Can you please add one?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EYou can find the full list of add on posting rules \u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154851-add-on-posting-rules-november-24-2017/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a very cool looking mod, I look forward to seeing more development!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EricPoehlsen","CreatedById":182872,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-09T23:08:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022123837\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dman979\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0The license is already included in the Readme.md - or does it have to be in a file of it\u0027s own?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-01-09T23:11:19Z\u0022 title=\u002201/09/2018 11:11  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by EricPoehlsen\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-09T23:16:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223264262\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022169414\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221515539318\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182872\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022EricPoehlsen\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, EricPoehlsen said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022123837\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/123837-dman979/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Dman979\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0The license is already included in the Readme.md - or does it have to be in a file of it\u0027s own?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor clarity\u0027s sake, it\u0027s best to put it in a file on its own.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs for this thread, something like \u0022This mod is licensed \u003Ca href=\u0022https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ECC BY-NC-ND 3.0\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u0022 (or any other appropriate license you chose) would be fine. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EricPoehlsen","CreatedById":182872,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-10T16:32:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome updates:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Part config includes TweakScale support\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Part was moved to \u0022Flight Control\u0022 in the tech tree\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Readme expanded\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"theonegalen","CreatedById":71012,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-05T19:45:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSounds great! I\u0027m going to give this a try in my new career save.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}